postgresql notes working with cloud 9

first 
pg_dropcluster --stop 9.3 main
pg_createcluster --start -e UTF-8 9.3 main
`sudo service postgresql start`

#postgesql comes with the user set us ubuntu so you have to reset it when your using an 
ubuntu devise.
sudo -u postgres dropuser ubuntu
sudo -u postgres createuser ubuntu -s

Then, you have to do a rails db:create
And of course you are going to have to do a rails db:migrate
